<br>
Against exp mobs I can chain nukes if I have my epic pet fighting; he'll generate enough taunt to protect me.<br>
<br>
Against HUGE (5+ min fight) uber mobs, I can glide through the fight and run out of mana by the end.<br>
<br>
The problem is on short (3- min) big mob fights. For me to go from full mana full life with a  mod rod 2 and mod rod 1 to out of mana and 40% life before the mob dies, I would SURELY overaggro and die. I simply can not run myself out of mana before the mob dies. <p>Master Cydmab Promethean, Triune <BR>
