<br>
In a drawn-out battle though, like the 10-minute enocunters you have mentioned, unless you go hard to OOM to start with, you'll be nuking with boots (optimum 35dps) and since uyoure standing the while time youll probably get say 35 mana/tick back with ubergear + AE bardsong + KEI + POTG.<br>
<br>
So you get to drop in a SoFB every minute or so which will bump your damage / minute by a grand (again assuming no resists).<br>
